clude the yellow top and light trousers, the light blue top with olive skirt, a beige top with dark shorts, and a pale green overshirt over a white outfit. The building’s large window grid fills the background. The product range returns on a pale mint surface: three boxed variants and a central bottle on a clear stand. The boxes show “Canna-B,” “Hyalu-Melon,” and “Pinea-C,” all under the Garnier Green Labs Serum Cream branding.\n\nThe commercial ends with the four women standing outdoors in front of lush green leaves and the fire escape. From left to right are the dark-skinned woman in yellow, the freckled woman in light blue, the short-haired woman in a dark top, and the woman in the pale green overshirt with her arms crossed. They stand close together, confident and relaxed, looking toward the viewer. A large green leaf circle with a white “G” appears over the lower centre of the group, then the white “GARNIER” brand name begins to appear across the bottom.",
